Maintainer: Niklas Hofer <niklas+cataract@lanpartei.de>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5)
Standards-Version: 3.7.2

Package: cataract-trayicon
Architecture: any
Depends: librexml-ruby
Description: gnome trayicon for cataract
 This package contains a (more or less) simple ruby script that shows
 a tray icon in the notification area.
 
 Now you can watch your downloading torrents with a simple mouse hovering.

 It will break on the first start, creating a config file in ~/.cataract.yml.
 Please edit this and start again.
